column6: FAMILY MATTERS PART 2 As Wiccan and Hulkling continue their quest to discover their ties to the Young Avengers, the rest of the team comes face to face with one of the most powerful alien races in the Marvel Universe!
column8: | penciller (cover):Jim Cheung | writer:Allan Heinberg | inker:Dave Meikis | letterer:Cory Petit | colorist:Justin Ponsor
